OL,4,COne Fastly customer triggered internet
OL,5,Cmeltdown
OL,6, A major internet blackout that hit many
OL,7, high-profile websites on Tuesday has
OL,8, been blamed on a software bug.
OL,10,FFastly, the cloud-computing company
OL,11,Fresponsible for the issues, said the
OL,12,Fbug had been triggered when one of its
OL,13,Fcustomers had changed their settings.
OL,15,FThe outage has raised questions about
OL,16,Frelying on a handful of companies to
OL,17,Frun the vast infrastructure that
OL,18,Funderpins the internet.
OL,20,FFastly apologised and said the problem
OL,21,Fshould have been anticipated.
